Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Bieble', 3: 'Are we finally close to the last checkpoint?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'With the checkpoint they had just passed emanating a green glow of completion, Bieble shifts his gaze toward the final one.'}

{3: 'The bright red reminder serves as a stark display of its inherent danger. However, the signal lights of all the strongholds surrounding it have gradually turned green, making it a desolate red island.'}
{3: 'They have woven a net of green, poised to defeat the red beast in its solitary abode.'}
{3: "Bieble casts a glance at his friend, who is now far behind. Although he wishes to extend a helping hand, he knows there's nothing he can do."}
{3: 'Freeman once likened Bieble to an animal that relies on instinct. Rather than devising elaborate plans, Bieble excels at improvisation.'}
{3: 'So unlike Freeman, he lacks the experience and speculations that are worth sharing with others.'}
{3: 'Despite an extensive search, Bieble still fails to find the name that always held a place in the top 10.'}
{3: 'Haniff appears to have settled into 10th place, with his ranking showing no signs of improvement or decline.'}
{3: 'Bieble closes the ranking page and opens the operation screen again.'}
